<plot>N.Y. fashion coordinator, Celia Davis, receives unexpected news - her mother, whom she has never known, has died suddenly and she's been appointed the guardian of her half-sister Merry, an uprooted twelve-year-old with an attitude and an airplane phobia. The cross-country trip that follows delivers many surprises, bringing Celia and Merry to a place that neither expected.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?133682</url></doc>
